      "id": "PopularPost54054",
      "post_content": "It's a nice card in any black red deck using creatures with come into play effects.  \nLike [chittering rats](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=chittering rats) or [hellhole rats](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=hellhole rats) or [flametongue kavu](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=flametongue kavu).  \n  \nManacurve wise, the best would be:  \nturn 2 [ravenous rats](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=ravenous rats)  \nturn 3 attack with rats, then play this zombie and return rats to hand  \nturn 4 attack with zombie, pump it by one and use the other 2 mana to replay the rats.  \nThen you have dealt 6 damage and made your opponent discard two cards by turn 4. It's not tournament quality but very solid for casual.  \n  \nIn the late game or slow multiplayer game, if the zombie get's killed, you can play a [gravedigger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=gravedigger) to get such a zombie back from your gy. Then replay it, return the gravedigger to hand, replay the digger, return another such zombie from your gy to hand until you have all lavazombies back, and then replay the digger another time for another creature.  \n  \nThe zombie needs badly trample though, so a au... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "majinara",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost54054\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">It's a nice card in any black red deck using creatures with come into play effects.<br/>Like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"chittering rats\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=chittering rats\">chittering rats</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"hellhole rats\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=hellhole rats\">hellhole rats</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"flametongue kavu\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=flametongue kavu\">flametongue kavu</a>.<br/><br/>Manacurve wise, the best would be:<br/>turn 2 <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"ravenous rats\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=ravenous rats\">ravenous rats</a><br/>turn 3 attack with rats, then play this zombie and return rats to hand<br/>turn 4 attack with zombie, pump it by one and use the other 2 mana to replay the rats.<br/>Then you have dealt 6 damage and made your opponent discard two cards by turn 4. It's not tournament quality but very solid for casual.<br/><br/>In the late game or slow multiplayer game, if the zombie get's killed, you can play a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"gravedigger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=gravedigger\">gravedigger</a> to get such a zombie back from your gy. Then replay it, return the gravedigger to hand, replay the digger, return another such zombie from your gy to hand until you have all lavazombies back, and then replay the digger another time for another creature.<br/><br/>The zombie needs badly trample though, so a au... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 54054)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '54054'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy555\">majinara</span>\r\n                                (2/17/2010 12:59:37 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
