      "id": "PopularPost41740",
      "post_content": "@ Donjohnson\n  \n   \nSadly it won't bring a creature from your graveyard to your hand, instead it requires you to bounce one of your creatures in play back to your hand (and if there are no others in play it will bounce its self).\n  \n   \nIf it had been the other way around it would have put [Gravedigger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gravedigger) to shame.\n  \n   \nIts no [undead warchief](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=undead warchief), but it isn't any [mindless null](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mindless null) either. Just an average zombie.",
      "posted_by": "Silverware",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost41740\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">@ Donjohnson\r<br/> <br/>Sadly it won't bring a creature from your graveyard to your hand, instead it requires you to bounce one of your creatures in play back to your hand (and if there are no others in play it will bounce its self). \r<br/> <br/>If it had been the other way around it would have put <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gravedigger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gravedigger\">Gravedigger</a> to shame.\r<br/> <br/>Its no <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"undead warchief\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=undead warchief\">undead warchief</a>, but it isn't any <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"mindless null\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=mindless null\">mindless null</a> either. Just an average zombie.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '41740'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2871\">Silverware</span>\r\n                                (12/21/2009 12:05:58 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=